fun.connor.lighter.compiler.generator

Class AbstractGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • fun.connor.lighter.compiler.generator.AbstractGenerator
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ControllerDataContainerGenerator, EndpointResolverGenerator, ReverseInjectorGenerator, RouteConfigurationGenerator

    public abstract class AbstractGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    Template class for Java class file generators. This class provides a template for generating classes during compile time and writing them to the build output. Implementations generate their type in the generateType() method and produce the package name of their type in the getGeneratedPackageName() method.
